snippet.title: Friday the 13th: Killer Puzzle Trailer
snippet.description:
Find out more: http://www.f13killerpuzzle.com

Available on iOS, Android, Steam, Switch, XBox, and PS4!

Jason Voorhees is Back for the Ultimate Experience in Bloody Puzzle Terror

Help horror icon Jason Voorhees stalk and slay campers across 100+ puzzle levels in this all-new game. From the campgrounds of Crystal Lake to the high-rises of Manhattan, from supermax prisons to snowy ski resorts, Jason will terrorize victims across the world... and beyond!
